lead_paragraph: Shaquille O'Neal was holding court at a press event during All-Star weekend, offering his analysis and opinions about all things NBA, when he was asked about Karl-Anthony Towns, the superb rookie of the Minnesota Timberwolves.

headline.print_headline: Young Timberwolves Have Their Coming-Out Party in W Over GSW
